1. *Hoću* da idem na more. (I *will* go to the seaside. )
2. Ona *neće* da jede povrće. (She *will not* eat vegetables. )
3. Da li *ćeš* ići sa mnom? (Will you go with me?)
4. *Hteo bih* da se zaposlim u toj firmi. (I *would like to* get a job in that company.)
5. Mi *ćemo* igrati fudbal u parku. (We *will* play soccer in the park.)
6. Oni *nisu hteli* da nam pomognu. (They *didn't want to* help us.)
7. *Hoćeš li* kafu ili čaj? (Do you want coffee or tea?)
8. On *ne bi hteo* da se oženi za nju. (He *would not like to* marry her.)
9. *Želeo bih* da putujem po svetu. (I *would like to* travel the world.)
10. *Mogao bih* da ti pomognem oko toga. (I *could* help you with that.)